title: Rambles with an American,
author: [Jacques, Edward Tyrell]
snippet: We walked up Windsor Street, and took the first turning to the right. This was Henley Street.

title: Rambles with an American,
author: [Jacques, Edward Tyrell]
snippet: But he checked himself before the sound had formed itself into a word and clutching my arm he hurried me away. He did not pause until we had turned the corner into Windsor Street.
